        "collapsible_tab_details": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Product Details",
            "content": "<p><strong>Material:</strong> High-density expanded polystyrene (EPS)<br\/><strong>Panel Size:</strong> 100cm x 50cm (0.5 m\u00b2 per panel)<br\/><strong>Thickness:</strong> 2 cm \/ ~1 inch<br\/><strong>Weight:</strong> Ultra-lightweight, approx. 100-200g per panel<br\/><strong>Fire Rating:</strong> Self-extinguishing material<br\/><strong>Moisture Resistance:</strong> Water-resistant, suitable for kitchens and bathrooms<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_thickness": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Thickness & Texture",
            "content": "<p>Each panel is 1 inch (2.54 cm) thick \u2014 this is genuine 3D depth, not a flat print or peel-and-stick surface. The raised brick pattern creates real shadow lines that shift with the light, giving your wall the appearance of authentic masonry. This is NOT wallpaper and NOT a sticker.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_install": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Installation Guide",
            "content": "<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Clean and dry your wall surface.<br\/><strong>Step 2:</strong> Apply construction adhesive to the back of each panel.<br\/><strong>Step 3:</strong> Press firmly onto the wall, hold for 30 seconds. Done.<\/p><p><em>Use a box cutter to trim panels at edges. No special tools needed. Optional: fix with screws for extra hold. Paint with any standard wall paint for a custom finish.<\/em><\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_shipping": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Shipping Info",
            "content": "<p>Manufacturing takes 2-3 days. Delivery generally takes 3-5 business days. Free shipping to the US and EU. Panels ship flat and lightweight. US, UK, EU, and Canada residents do not pay customs fees or import taxes.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_faq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "FAQ",
            "content": "<p><strong>Can I paint these?<\/strong><br\/>Yes \u2014 any standard interior wall paint works. Use a roller or spray for best results.<\/p><p><strong>Outdoor use?<\/strong><br\/>Yes. Our panels are moisture-resistant and weather-resistant.<\/p><p><strong>How many panels per m\u00b2?<\/strong><br\/>Each panel covers 0.5 m\u00b2 (100cm x 50cm), so 2 panels per square meter.<\/p><p><strong>How do I cut them?<\/strong><br\/>A standard box cutter or utility knife cuts through easily along a straight edge.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
