    "testimonials": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial-0": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>I finished our accent wall in one afternoon. The texture looks far more expensive than it is. Every guest asks who designed it.<\/p>",
            "author": "Ayse K. \u2014 Istanbul",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "testimonial-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>We wanted the look of old brick without the weight. These panels gave the room instant character and were incredibly simple to install.<\/p>",
            "author": "Mehmet D. \u2014 Ankara",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "testimonial-2": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>The finish photographs beautifully and looks even better in person. Turned a plain wall into the focal point of the apartment.<\/p>",
            "author": "Sarah L. \u2014 London",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "testimonial-3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>Ordered 40 panels for our restaurant entrance. The brick effect looks completely real. Installation was easy and the result is stunning.<\/p>",
            "author": "Marco R. \u2014 Milan",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "testimonial-4": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>Best wall upgrade we've ever done. Painted them to match our bedroom palette and the 3D effect is incredible. Highly recommend.<\/p>",
            "author": "Emma W. \u2014 New York",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        }
      },
